	<string>AdsyClub continuously shares your GPS location in the background while you are active as a rideshare driver, so passengers can find you on the map and you can receive nearby ride requests. Background location is only active when you enable Driver Mode in the Rideshare section.</string>
	<key>NSLocationAlwaysUsageDescription</key>
	<string>AdsyClub continuously shares your GPS location in the background while you are active as a rideshare driver, so passengers can find you on the map and you can receive nearby ride requests. Background location is only active when you enable Driver Mode in the Rideshare section.</string>

